highlights.text: “Whenever (feat. Conor Maynard)” by Kris Kross Amsterdam, The Boy Next Door, and Conor Maynard is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 73 spots at #127.
“Closer” by The Chainsmokers and Halsey has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 85 weeks straight.
